few posts have been right on and the quest is not<BR>
all that hard. I remember waiting 2 weeks to get<BR>
3 BB casks for my Jagged Pine Cloak!!!! Good luck<BR>
to all you Rangers that are doing this quest. The<BR>
bow is more than worth the time. You just can't<BR>
